local espConnections,espHighlights,espNameTags={},{},{};local function createPlayerESP(p)local char=p.Character or p.CharacterAdded:Wait();local hrp=char:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart");if not hrp then return end;local h=Instance.new("Highlight");h.Name="WindUI_ESP";h.Adornee=char;h.FillColor=Color3.new(1,0,0);h.FillTransparency=0.5;h.OutlineTransparency=0;h.DepthMode=Enum.HighlightDepthMode.AlwaysOnTop;h.Parent=char;espHighlights[p]=h;local nt=Instance.new("BillboardGui");nt.Name="WindUI_NameTag";nt.Adornee=hrp;nt.Size=UDim2.new(0,150,0,20);nt.StudsOffset=Vector3.new(0,2.8,0);nt.AlwaysOnTop=true;nt.Parent=hrp;local tl=Instance.new("TextLabel");tl.Size=UDim2.new(1,0,1,0);tl.BackgroundTransparency=1;tl.Text=p.Name;tl.TextColor3=Color3.new(1,1,1);tl.Font=Enum.Font.SourceSansBold;tl.TextSize=14;tl.TextScaled=false;tl.Parent=nt;espNameTags[p]=nt end;local function removePlayerESP(p)if espHighlights[p]and espHighlights[p].Parent then espHighlights[p]:Destroy();espHighlights[p]=nil end;if espNameTags[p]and espNameTags[p].Parent then espNameTags[p]:Destroy();espNameTags[p]=nil end end;local function togglePlayerESP(s)if s then for _,p in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers())do if p~=LP then pcall(createPlayerESP,p)end end;espConnections.playerAdded=Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(p)p.CharacterAdded:Wait();pcall(createPlayerESP,p)end);espConnections.playerRemoving=Players.PlayerRemoving:Connect(function(p)removePlayerESP(p)end)else if espConnections.playerAdded then espConnections.playerAdded:Disconnect()end;if espConnections.playerRemoving then espConnections.playerRemoving:Disconnect()end;for p,_ in pairs(espHighlights)do removePlayerESP(p)end;espHighlights={};espNameTags={}end end
